Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:53.57,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Though I know that you're a great liar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:57.24,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}The world is painted in dark grey
