Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:11.93,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}どうか貴方の未来へと陰落とさぬ様に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:19.35,OP-Jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(0,500,\c&H030171&)}Going down to reach somewhere together
